.TH "LIGHTNING-BALANCE" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-balance \- on-chain + LN balance, recfile
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning balance
[\fIsubcommand\fR] [\fIargs\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.nf
lightning balance — on-chain + LN balance, recfile.

Implements: clightning listfunds reshape per FEAT-171.

Default output (three-line recfile):
  onchain_confirmed_sat: <sat>
  onchain_unconfirmed_sat: <sat>
  channels_sat: <sat>

Flags:
  --on-chain   print the on-chain receive address from clightning's
               `newaddr` instead. Useful when funding the LN node.
.fi
.SH "SEE ALSO"
.BR lightning (1)
.SH AUTHOR
Part of the \fBlightning\fR educational Lightning Network frontend.
